<item>
            <title>[LU-1263] 2.1.1&lt;-&gt;2.2 OST0000 cannot be mounted after sanity test_27z failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1263</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity subtest 51b hang after subtest 27z failed. The OST0000 cannot be mounted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OST dmesg:&lt;br/&gt;
--------------------&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@fat-intel-4 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# LustreError: 4319:0:(ldlm_lib.c:2129:target_send_reply_msg()) @@@ processing error (&lt;del&gt;19)  req@ffff88032a885000 x1397613683283791/t0(0) o-1&lt;/del&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;?&amp;gt;@&amp;lt;?&amp;gt;:0/0 lens 368/0 e 0 to 0 dl 1332872055 ref 1 fl Interpret:/ffffffff/ffffffff rc -19/-1&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 4319:0:(ldlm_lib.c:2129:target_send_reply_msg()) Skipped 357 previous similar messages&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: 137-5: UUID &apos;lustre-OST0000_UUID&apos; is not available  for connect (no target)&lt;br/&gt;
LustreError: Skipped 357 previous similar messages&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@fat-intel-4 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# mount&lt;br/&gt;
/dev/sda1 on / type ext3 (rw)&lt;br/&gt;
