/dev/sdb2 on /mnt/ost2 type lustre (rw)&lt;br/&gt;
/dev/sdb3 on /mnt/ost3 type lustre (rw)&lt;br/&gt;
/dev/sdc1 on /mnt/ost4 type lustre (rw)&lt;br/&gt;
